description: Welcome to this stunning 2-bed condo, built in 2020. Located in a professionally managed boutique 8-unit elevator building with garage parking, this modern home boasts an open layout with high ceilings and an abundance of natural light. The kitchen is a chef’s dream, featuring gas cooking, a custom-built island with seating for four, quartz countertops, and a marble backsplash. The spacious master bedroom includes a walk-in closet, while the full bathroom is equipped with luxurious heated floors. Enjoy outdoor living on your private deck with a gas hookup, perfect for grilling. Additional highlights include wide plank European oak flooring, central ac, and the convenience of new construction.  Located in South Boston’s sought after City Point neighborhood, this home is a short walk to Castle Island, the beach, and Seaport district.  A true gem this one is not to be missed!!
